extendedInfo.description: Have you ever needed to access your Medicaid member benefits but not had time to call? Would you like to find a provider near you when youâre on the go? This is the app for that! Welcome to myHealthButton â a free mobile app that gives you real-time access to your Child Special Health Care Services (CSHCS), Women, Infants & Children (WIC), or Medicaid benefits instantly and securely in the palm of your hand! From receiving reminders and educational alerts to the ability to search for a provider âNear Me,â this application simplifies beneficiary interaction with the Medicaid system. If you are a currently enrolled Medicaid member, you can log in and view your benefits. If you are a guardian or the head of your household, you can view your dependentâs information as well! Features - General Medicaid Features - View your or your dependent's Benefits - View your Medicaid Card - View and update your Other Insurance Information - Fee-for-Service Beneficiaries can find Medicaid Providers âNear Meâ or by a customized search - Childrenâs Special Health Care Services - View your Qualifying Diagnoses - View Authorized Providers - Women, Infants & Children - View your real-time Food Benefits Balance - Receive Alerts - Reminders for Appointments - Educational Tips - System Alerts - Customize It! - Set up text messaging to receive your alerts on your phone - Add, modify or remove beneficiaries Safe and Secure: myHealthButton has all the advanced security you would expect for an application containing your private health information. We have implemented safety features currently in use by the banking industry. - Access to your data is protected by Level 3 Authentication Standards per NIST (National Institute of Standards and Technology). - All data sent to or from your phone are secured. - Multiple levels of authentication are performed upon registration and log in to verify your user and beneficiary information. - No health information is stored on your phone â ever. - Session timeouts ensure no one can access your information if you are away from your phone for an extended time.

reviews.title: No WIC?
reviews.comment: I downloaded this specifically for access to my son\'s WIC benefits. The app provides good access to his Medicade info, but no WIC info is present anywhere in the app that I could find. Also, the app is a little slow as it is a straight port from iOS.
